3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a new neural network architecture for object detection, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The proposed method involves using collective evidence from all the points on the objects of interest, which is a common approach in artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language): Although less likely, the paper involves some natural language processing in terms of the way the authors describe their proposed method and the results.
